.186" end="00:25.493">bill,</span> <span begin="00:25.493" end="00:26.393">y'all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">钞票，钞票啊，兄弟们</span></p><p begin="00:26.627" end="00:29.526" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:26.627" end="00:26.781">I</span> <span begin="00:26.781" end="00:26.984">grew</span> <span begin="00:26.984" end="00:27.289">up</span> <span begin="00:27.289" end="00:27.437">on</span> <span begin="00:27.437" end="00:27.624">the</span> <span begin="00:27.624" end="00:27.980">crime</span> <span begin="00:27.980" end="00:28.331">side,</span> <span begin="00:28.331" end="00:28.457">the</span> <span begin="00:28.457" end="00:28.623">New</span> <span begin="00:28.623" end="00:28.955">York</span> <span begin="00:28.955" end="00:29.282">Times</span> <span begin="00:29.282" end="00:29.526">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我在犯罪街区长大，纽约街头的乱世里</span></p><p begin="00:29.815" end="00:31.254" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:29.815" end="00:29.963">Stay</span><span begin="00:29.963" end="00:30.132">in'</span> <span begin="00:30.132" end="00:30.281">a</span><span begin="00:30.281" end="00:30.668">live</span> <span begin="00:30.668" end="00:30.791">was</span> <span begin="00:30.791" end="00:31.039">no</span> <span begin="00:31.039" end="00:31.254">jive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">活下去从不是儿戏</span></p><p begin="00:31.488" end="00:34.370" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:31.488" end="00:31.754">Had</span> <span begin="00:31.754" end="00:31.924">se</span><span begin="00:31.924" end="00:32.121">cond</span> <span begin="00:32.121" end="00:32.589">hands,</span> <span begin="00:32.807" end="00:33.136">Mom's</span> <span begin="00:33.136" end="00:33.430">bounced</span> <span begin="00:33.430" end="00:33.679">on</span> <span begin="00:33.679" end="00:33.962">old</span> <span begin="00:33.962" end="00:34.370">man</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">家里穷得叮当响，老妈离开了老爸</span></p><p begin="00:34.691" end="00:36.490" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:34.691" end="00:34.791">So</span> <span begin="00:34.791" end="00:34.949">then</span> <span begin="00:34.949" end="00:35.136">we</span> <span begin="00:35.136" end="00:35.451">moved</span> <span begin="00:35.451" end="00:35.629">to</span> <span begin="00:35.629" end="00:35.948">Shao</span><span begin="00:35.948" end="00:36.100">lin</span> <span begin="00:36.100" end="00:36.490">land</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">于是我们搬去了少林（斯塔滕岛）</span></p><p begin="00:36.690" end="00:39.709" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:36.690" end="00:36.781">A</span> <span begin="00:36.781" end="00:37.052">young</span> <span begin="00:37.052" end="00:37.398">youth,</span> <span begin="00:37.679" end="00:37.826">yo,</span> <span begin="00:37.826" end="00:38.049">ro</span><span begin="00:38.049" end="00:38.163">ckin'</span> <span begin="00:38.163" end="00:38.311">the</span> <span begin="00:38.311" end="00:38.622">gold</span> <span begin="00:38.622" end="00:38.912">tooth,</span> <span begin="00:39.135" end="00:39.444">'Lo</span> <span begin="00:39.444" end="00:39.709">goose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">年少轻狂，镶着金牙，穿着 Polo 外套</span></p><p begin="00:39.806" end="00:42.342" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="00:39.806" end="00:39.942">On</span><span begin="00:39.942" end="00:40.110">ly</span> <span begin="00:40.110" end="00:40.278">way</span> <span begin="00:40.499" end="00:40.629">I</span> <span begin="00:40.629" end="00:40.807">be</span><span begin="00:40.807" end="00:40.952">gin</span> <span begin="00:40.952" end="00:41.150">the</span> <span begin="00:41.150" end="00:41.318">G</span> <span begin="00:41.318" end="00:41.629">off</span> <span begin="00:41.629" end="00:41.788">was</span> <span begin="00:41.788" end="00:42.101">drug</span> <span begin="00:42.101" end="00:42.342">loot</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-